{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "familyroots-api-local",
    "name": "FamilyRoots API",
    "description": "Family Tree API — Part 0–5.\n\n**Flow:** Auth → Login → Persons → Logs.\n\n**Error format:** `{ \"error\": { \"code\", \"message\" } }`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "General",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Root — API info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/",
            "description": "**200 OK**\n```json\n{ \"data\": { \"name\": \"Family Tree API\", \"version\": \"v1\" } }\n```"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health",
            "description": "**200 OK** `{ \"status\": \"ok\" }`"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Login dengan kode keluarga `{ABBREV}{DDMMYY}`. Contoh seed: `KAMU210399` (demo utama), `MR170845`, `AYAH200175`.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login — demo MR170845",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('personId', String(json.data.person.id));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"MR170845\",\n  \"remember\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "description": "**Public** — login Mulyono Raka (demo-mr).\n\n| Field | Type | Required |\n|---|---|---|\n| code | string | yes |\n| remember | boolean | no (default false) |\n\n**200 OK**\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"accessToken\": \"...\",\n    \"refreshToken\": \"...\",\n    \"expiresIn\": 3600,\n    \"person\": {\n      \"id\": 95,\n      \"fullName\": \"Mulyono Raka\",\n      \"nickname\": null,\n      \"gender\": \"male\",\n      \"birthDate\": \"1945-08-17\",\n      \"status\": \"alive\",\n      \"photoUrl\": null\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Errors:**\n- 400 `CODE_REQUIRED`\n- 400 `CODE_INVALID_FORMAT`\n- 401 `CODE_NOT_FOUND`\n- 429 `TOO_MANY_ATTEMPTS`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — me KAMU210399",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('personId', String(json.data.person.id));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"KAMU210399\",\n  \"remember\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — invalid format",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"ABC\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "description": "Expect **400** `CODE_INVALID_FORMAT`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — code not found",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"XXXX010100\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "description": "Expect **401** `CODE_NOT_FOUND` (sama untuk deceased)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me",
            "description": "**Auth required**\n\n**200 OK**\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 95,\n    \"fullName\": \"...\",\n    \"nickname\": null,\n    \"gender\": \"male\",\n    \"birthDate\": \"1945-08-17\",\n    \"status\": \"alive\",\n    \"photoUrl\": null,\n    \"familyId\": 1\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**401** `UNAUTHORIZED` tanpa/invalid token"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh",
            "description": "**Public** — rotate refresh token.\n\n**200 OK** `{ accessToken, refreshToken, expiresIn }`\n\n**401** `REFRESH_TOKEN_INVALID`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout",
            "description": "**Auth required** — revoke refresh token.\n\n**200 OK** `{ \"data\": { \"loggedOut\": true } }`"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Logs",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Track page view",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"action\": \"page.view\",\n  \"path\": \"/tree\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/logs/events",
            "description": "**201 Created** `{ \"data\": { \"recorded\": true } }`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Track click",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"action\": \"click\",\n  \"path\": \"/tree\",\n  \"label\": \"Buka profil ayah\",\n  \"metadata\": { \"targetPersonId\": 42 }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/logs/events"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Track event — invalid payload",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"action\": \"invalid\",\n  \"path\": \"\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/logs/events",
            "description": "Expect **400** `INVALID_LOG_EVENT`"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "CORS (Part 4)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Preflight OPTIONS /auth/login",
          "request": {
            "method": "OPTIONS",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Origin", "value": "http://localhost:5173" },
              { "key": "Access-Control-Request-Method", "value": "POST" },
              { "key": "Access-Control-Request-Headers", "value": "Content-Type, Authorization" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "description": "Expect **204** with `Access-Control-Allow-Origin` when origin is listed in `CORS_ORIGINS`."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Persons (Part 5)",
      "description": "Semua endpoint butuh `Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}`. Response camelCase + `generationLabel`/`isSelf` dinamis dari user login.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List persons (paginated)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/persons?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "persons"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "**200 OK** — mode list (default).\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"view\": \"list\",\n    \"rootPersonId\": 83,\n    \"persons\": [ /* max 20 */ ],\n    \"pagination\": {\n      \"page\": 1,\n      \"limit\": 20,\n      \"total\": 95,\n      \"totalPages\": 5,\n      \"hasNext\": true,\n      \"hasPrev\": false\n    }\n  }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List persons (tree graph)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/persons?view=tree",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "persons"],
              "query": [{ "key": "view", "value": "tree" }]
            },
            "description": "**200 OK** — semua person untuk render pohon (tanpa pagination).\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"view\": \"tree\",\n    \"rootPersonId\": 83,\n    \"persons\": [ /* all 95 */ ],\n    \"treeGraph\": {\n      \"anchorPersonId\": 83,\n      \"edgeFields\": { \"parent\": [\"fatherId\", \"motherId\"], \"spouse\": \"spouseIds\" },\n      \"note\": \"...\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\nLihat `docs/PERSON-API-TREE.md`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get person by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/persons/{{personId}}",
            "description": "Detail satu person dalam family scope."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create person",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Anak Baru Demo\",\n  \"gender\": \"male\",\n  \"birthDate\": \"2026-01-01\",\n  \"status\": \"alive\",\n  \"fatherId\": null,\n  \"motherId\": null,\n  \"spouseIds\": []\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/persons",
            "description": "**201 Created** — login code derived otomatis dari nama+tanggal."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update person",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Anak Baru Demo Updated\",\n  \"gender\": \"male\",\n  \"birthDate\": \"2026-01-01\",\n  \"status\": \"alive\",\n  \"nickname\": \"Demo\",\n  \"spouseIds\": []\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/persons/{{personId}}",
            "description": "**200 OK** — update person dalam family."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete person",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/persons/99999",
            "description": "Soft delete. **403** jika hapus diri sendiri sebagai root family."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List without token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/persons",
            "description": "Expect **401** `UNAUTHORIZED`"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Errors (examples)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Not found",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/does-not-exist",
            "description": "Expect **404** `NOT_FOUND`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me without token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me",
            "description": "Expect **401** `UNAUTHORIZED`"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
